 My issue is as follows
My game has been experiencing incredibly high ping  (~800 ping), with the bare minimum settings,  when no other system in the house that can connect to the internet is on. 

Whereas I can play Dota with 45 ping with YouTube, Facebook, Reddit, Steam, and all my various devices open and connected to the internet. I hate this because I love the game to death. But when I can run Dota, Cities Skylines and Just Cause 3 with high graphic settings without hinderance; I am assured there is a definite problem Riot-side.  {{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}

